{"title":"红旗舒展","authors":["友田"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":11,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五颗金星亮在蓝天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每朵花里都有您的芬芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每滴水里都有您的笑颜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您舒展着中华的风采"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您漫卷着赤子的思恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您用爱覆盖神州大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您把情洒向百姓心田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要那支歌轰然响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国旗下便闪动双双泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼红旗舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰刀铁锤金光闪闪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每条船上都有您的双桨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每座塔上都有您的灯盏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您牢记着人类的解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您呼唤着历史的巨变"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您指挥我们英勇奋战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您领导我们创造明天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要那支歌轰然响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗下便耸立一丛铁拳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八一”金辉普照河山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每片叶里都有您的蓬勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每排浪里都有您的勇敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您就是牢不可破的钢铁长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您就是不容侵犯的祖国尊严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您仰望南昌夜空的星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您升起北京黎明的鲜艳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要那支歌轰然响起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军旗下便展示忠心赤胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗舒展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何等潇洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何等威严"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何等壮观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这血与火的颜色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是力量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是源泉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}